---
// Visual: Agentic Loop Diagram
---
<div class="space-y-6">
  <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted">The Agentic Loop</p>

  <div class="relative p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface">
    <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 text-accent flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">1</span>
        <div>
          <span class="text-text-primary font-semibold">Read</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted ml-2">files, errors, context</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-4 border-l border-border h-4"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 text-accent flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">2</span>
        <div>
          <span class="text-text-primary font-semibold">Think</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted ml-2">analyze, plan approach</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-4 border-l border-border h-4"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 text-accent flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">3</span>
        <div>
          <span class="text-text-primary font-semibold">Act</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted ml-2">edit, run commands</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-4 border-l border-border h-4"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 text-accent flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">4</span>
        <div>
          <span class="text-text-primary font-semibold">Verify</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted ml-2">test, check output</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-4 border-l border-dashed border-accent h-4"></div>
      <div class="text-xs text-accent text-center">↩ repeat until done</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface/50">
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Built-in Tools</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs">
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Read files</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Edit code</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Run bash</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Search code</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Web fetch</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-background rounded text-text-secondary">Git operations</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
